data.title: SXSW 2024 Schedule
data.meta_description: SXSW 2024 Schedule | The entrepreneurial mindset - is it something you’re born with or something you can cultivate? After 40 years in business, Michael Dell is sharing his thoughts on risk taking, having the courage of your conviction, reinvention, and the magic of Austin. A technology optimist at heart, this session will also discuss today’s hottest tech trends including the opportunities we have with AI and how it will transform industries.
data.text: The entrepreneurial mindset - is it something you’re born with or something you can cultivate? After 40 years in business, Michael Dell is sharing his thoughts on risk taking, having the courage of your conviction, reinvention, and the magic of Austin.
